Package: subtitleburner
Version: 1.0.0
Section: video
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-venv, python3-pip, ffmpeg, nodejs, npm, python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-3.0, gir1.2-webkit2-4.1 | gir1.2-webkit2-4.0
Maintainer: Subtitle Burner <noreply@example.com>
Description: Automatic subtitle generation, translation, and burning
 Subtitle Burner transcribes speech in a video using Whisper, optionally
 translates the subtitles, and produces a video with them either burned in
 or embedded as a selectable track. Ships with a web UI, a native desktop
 GUI, and a terminal UI.
 .
 First launch downloads several GB of additional dependencies (PyTorch,
 speech/translation models) and needs an internet connection.
